    {
      "question": "<p>Factorise<br /><u>(a + 2) + 4(a + 2)</u></p>",
      "choices": [
        "*(a + 2)(1 + 4) = 5(a + 2)",
        "(a + 2)(4) = 4(a + 2) ",
        "5a + 4",
        "4(a + 2)"
      ],
      "id": "math/03.5",
      "explain": "<p>Je mets en evidence le facteur commun<br /><span style=\"color: #e74c3c;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">(a + 1) </span></span>x <span style=\"color: #2880b9;\">1 </span>+ <span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">(a + 1) </span>x <span style=\"color: #2880b9;\">4</span></p>\n<p>J'applique la formule<br />AxB + AxC = A(B + C)<br />avec A = (a + 2), B = 1 et C = 4<br /><br />=<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">(a + 1)</span> (<span style=\"color: #2880b9;\">1</span> + <span style=\"color: #2880b9;\">4</span>)<br />=5(a+1)</p>"
    },
