    {
      "question": "<p>On souhaite factoriser</p>\n<p><u>(x+3)(3x+4)+(x+3)(x-9).</u></p>\n<p>On remarque que le facteur commun est (x+3).<br />L'expression factoris&eacute;e sera donc de la forme (x+3)(.......).</p>\n<p>Que vaut ....... ?</p>",
      "choices": [
        "*3x + 4 + x - 9",
        "x + 3 + x - 9",
        "3x + 4  + x + 3",
        "3x + 4"
      ],
      "id": "math/03.8",
      "explain": "<p>On utilise la formule:<br /><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">AxB + AxC = A(B + C)</span></p>\n<p>avec A = (x+3), B = 3x +4 et C = x-9).</p>\n<p>= (x+3)(<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">3x + 4 + x - 9</span>)&nbsp;</p>"
    },
    {
      "question": "<p>On souhaite factoriser</p>\n<p><u>(x-7)(3x+4)-(x-7)(x-9)</u></p>\n<p>On remarque que le facteur commun est (x-7). L'expression factoris&eacute;e sera donc de la forme (x-7)(.......).</p>\n<p>Que vaut ...... ?</p>",
      "choices": [
        "*3x + 4 - x + 9",
        "3x + 4 - x - 9"
      ],
      "id": "math/03.9",
      "explain": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">(x-7)<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">(3x+4) </span>- (x-7)<span style=\"color: #9b59b6;\">(x-9)</span><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">=(x - 7)( <span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">(3x+ 4)</span> - <span style=\"color: #9b59b6;\">(x-9)</span> )<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">=(x - 7)(3x + 4 - x <span style=\"color: #e74c3c;\"><strong>+</strong></span> 9)<br /><br />Attention:<br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #e74c3c;\">-(x - 9) = -x + 9</span></strong><u><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><br /></span></u></p>"
    },
    {
      "question": "<p>Factorise l'expression</p>\n<p><u> (1-5x)(x+5)+(x+5)&sup2;</u></p>",
      "choices": [
        "*(x+5)(1 - 5x + x + 5)",
        "(x+5)(1 - 5x + 1)",
        "(x+5)(1 - 5x)"
      ],
      "id": "math/03.10",
      "explain": "<p>Il faut ecrire&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">(x+5)&sup2; sous forme </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">(x+5)(x +5)&nbsp;<br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">=</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">(1-5x)(x+5)+(x+5)</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">(x+5)</span></span><u><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><br /><br /></span></u><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">Applique la formule</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">AxB + AxC = A(B + C)</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><br /></span><u><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><br />=(x + 5)(1 - 5x + x + 5)<br /></span></u></p>"
