      "id": "math/03.12",
      "explain": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;x&sup2;+4x+4 ressemble a:<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #3598db;\">&nbsp;a&sup2;+2ab+b</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">&sup2;</span> avec a=x, b=2</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #e67e23;\">= x&sup2; + 2 . 2 . x +2</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">&sup2;</span><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">= (x + 2)</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">&sup2;</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><br /><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></p>"
    },
    {
      "question": "<p>Quelle est la forme factoris&eacute;e de</p>\n<p><u>25 - 16p&sup2;</u></p>",
      "choices": [
        "*(5 + 4p)(5 - 4p)",
        "(5 + 4p)(5 + 4p)",
        "(25 + 16p)(25 - 16p)",
        "(5 + 16p)(5 - 16p)"
      ],
      "id": "math/03.13",
      "explain": "<p>J'utilise:&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">a</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">&sup2;</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"> - b</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">&sup2; = (a - b)(a + b)</span><br /><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">25 - <span style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">16p</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">&sup2;</span> = 5</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">&sup2; - <span style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">(4p)</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #e74c3c;\">&sup2;<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">Attention aux parentheses autour du carre!<br /><br />=(5 - 4p)(5 + 4p)</span></p>"
    },
